;SHEET
THE TWO SHEETS PRESENTED AS *BAA* AND *BAB* ON SHEET
RECORDS BELOW ARE ACTUALLY EIGHT-STRANDED BETA-BARRELS.
EACH IS REPRESENTED BY A NINE-STRANDED SHEET IN WHICH THE
FIRST AND LAST STRANDS ARE IDENTICAL.
;
